[OVERLAY] VimFu — :%norm — Normal on Every Line
[SAY] Colon norm runs normal mode keystrokes on lines. Percent norm runs on every line in the file.
[SAY] These JavaScript lines are missing semicolons. Let's add one to every line.
[TYPE] ':%norm A;'

